data.description: Adorable White Brick Bungalow COMPLETELY REHABBED featuring 4 bedrooms and 3 full baths!! Warm neutral colors throughout this charming and welcoming home. Gleaming hardwood floors on main level with 2 bedrooms.  Bathrooms have all been remodeled with high end fixtures and amazing tile work.  Kitchen is a chefs dream with all new stainless steel appliances, cherry colored cabinets, granite counter tops with decorative back splash. 2 bedrooms on main level or   Retire to the second floor huge MASTER SUITE WITH  MASTER BATH. Enjoy even more space in the finished basement with a large family room, another bedroom, great size laundry room PLUS a 2 car garage, nice size backyard with lots of curb appeal.  Bring your buyers to this one it will not last long on the market.  Fabulous REHAB!!
